                        <additions>
                          <list>
                            <item xml:id="a1">
                               <locus from="130ra" to="130rb"/>
                               <desc type="DonationNote"/>The original note (written in a hand
                               different from the main <ref target="#h1">Hand 1</ref>) was in part erased, and
                               new names were inserted (written in a hand similar,
                               but not identical to the main hand).
                                In its new version (not well readable), the note states that the manuscript was donated by <persName ref="PRS13842WaldaWahed">Walda Wāḥǝd</persName> to
                               the church or monastery of <placeName ref="LOC7366DabraGiyorgis">Dabra Giyorgis</placeName> in the district called
                               <placeName ref="LOC7365Gucari">Guč̣āri</placeName>. The name of the
                               donor is extended by a traditional genealogy.
                                 <q xml:lang="gez"></q>
