                    <history>
                        <origin>
                     <origDate notBefore="1770" notAfter="1849">Late 18th/first half of
                       the 19th century</origDate>.
                       The names of the original commissioners or owners have been erased from the supplication
                       formulas. Names of other individuals have been written instead, such as
                       <persName ref="PRS13844ZawgaMikael" role="owner"/>,
                       his son <persName ref="PRS13842WaldaWahed" role="owner"/>,
                          <persName ref="PRS13843GabraWahed" role="owner"/> and others (possibly belonging to
                          the same family). <ref target="#a1">Additional note 1</ref> seems to tell that
                          <persName ref="PRS13844ZawgaMikael" role="donor"/> donated the manuscript to
                          <placeName ref="LOC7366DabraGiyorgis">Dabra Giyorgis</placeName> in the district <placeName ref="LOC7365Gucari">Guč̣āri</placeName>.
                          </origin>
                        <provenance>The manuscript was acquired by
